Rip notes: Edited Audio

Wacky races with Claymation style animal characters is the order of the day. Choose from 8 cutesy crazy creatures including penguins, sharks, walrus & squid each with their own attributes.

There are 4 tracks, each track has 5 variations for you to test each creatures skills. Each race consists of 3 legs, Waddling, Swimming and then finally Belly Sliding, across strange themed landscapes.

Bored with the way your racer looks, no problem because you can customise the way the animals look with all sorts of accessories like shoes & hats and even a machine gun.

Simple controls make this a fun racer for young and old, for up 4 players.